nspired by every single day we seek each other’s opinions and ideas share in our success and learn from our failures we achieve more together than we ever could on our own benefits investing in your growth continuous learning our dedicated learning  development team matches employees with industry experts to provide personalized skill development team members are encouraged to pursue advanced degrees nourish  energize healthy foods and snacks keep our teams at peak performance after hours exclusive events for colleagues friends and family from box seats at stadiums to theater buyouts and cooking classes you’ll bond with colleagues at global and local events onsite fitness centers reach new levels of personal performance with access to fitness centers what our people say results of  great place to work survey  say colleagues are willing to give extra to get the job done  of employees say they are proud to tell others they work here  feel a sense of pride when they look at what we accomplish  say they feel welcomed when they joined the company  say the firm is a friendly place to work  say they are given a lot of responsibility supporting our communities new computer labs at carnegie mellon partnering with carnegie mellon university citadel helped create the stateoftheart citadel teaching commons support includes technology to support research in machine learning distributed systems and parallel computing architecture read more kenneth griffin makes largest gift in harvard college history alumnus donates  million to principally support financial aid read more citadel service day more than  citadel team members joined together with family and friends to volunteer on citadel service day  citadel serves we help our communities reach their full potential by creating meaningful sustainable outcomes while financial support is part of our effort the heart of citadel serves is our employees’ commitment to sharing their time and expertise last year our colleagues contributed m